## Problem

What are you trying to accomplish? What gets in the way today?

## Proposed solution

What you'd like to see. Be specific — "add an export feature" is hard to act on; "add a `Page → Export to PDF` menu item that calls X" is easy.

## Alternatives you considered

What else could solve the underlying problem? Any existing workarounds?

## Fit with project principles

Before requesting, please skim [`docs/PROJECT.md`](../docs/PROJECT.md) "Principles" and "Non-goals". If the request conflicts with either, explain why it should still be considered.

## Anything else?

Mockups, references to similar features in other tools, or related discussions.
